    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver 414 hp with a linear power band peaking at its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from its weight-optimized aluminum multi-link suspension and Electronic Damper Control (EDC). Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the longitudinal and lateral dynamics remain uncompromised. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its age, the performance envelope remains sharp and visceral. A purist\u2019s specification for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
